Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:39.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fs50\pos(1055,1010)}Necro
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:42.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}苦しみだけ置いていくはず
